'''劍獅'''是[[臺灣|臺灣]]一種避邪物，該避邪物尤其多見於臺南[[安平區|安平地區]]一帶，為當地傳統民宅門[[簷|簷]]及[[照壁|照壁]]上之常見裝飾<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dsps.chc.edu.tw/tuling/anc2/0qrg1.htm|title=安平劍獅|accessdate=2017-01-13|work=www.dsps.chc.edu.tw|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224162108/http://www.dsps.chc.edu.tw/tuling/anc2/0qrg1.htm|archivedate=2016-12-24}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20150416/589723/|title=林于昉：安平劍獅神祕力量 {{!}} 即時新聞 {{!}} 20150416 {{!}} 蘋果日報|newspaper=蘋果日報|accessdate=2017-01-13|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2017-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116153749/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20150416/589723/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.anpingstay.com/%E5%AE%89%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E7%A5%9E-%E5%8A%8D%E7%8D%85/|title=安平守護神 劍獅|date=2015-03-27|newspaper=來住安平|accessdate=2017-01-13|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2017-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118081629/http://www.anpingstay.com/%E5%AE%89%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E7%A5%9E-%E5%8A%8D%E7%8D%85/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aloc/201608280017-1.aspx|title=結合在地文化  安平郵局劍獅郵筒夯 {{!}} 地方 {{!}} 中央社即時新聞 CNA NEWS|last=中央通訊社|accessdate=2017-01-13|archive-date=2017-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116155820/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aloc/201608280017-1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。目前，隨著安平地區民居大多逐漸翻新，該種塑像之數量及樣貌已發生改變<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.flyingv.cc/projects/10742|title=即將消失的文化資產—安平劍獅 {{!}} flyingV|accessdate=2017-01-13|work=flyingV|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2017-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116152825/https://www.flyingv.cc/projects/10742|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|last=大愛電視 Tzu Chi DaAiVideo|title=【發現】20150905 - 安平曲巷 - 尋劍獅|date=2015-09-05|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MtG5op1hX7U|accessdate=2017-01-13}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://roryjen.pixnet.net/blog/post/27874442-%E5%AE%89%E5%B9%B3%E5%8A%8D%E7%8D%85%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85%EF%BC%8D%E9%81%8D%E5%B0%8B%E4%B8%8D%E8%91%97%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%8D%E7%8D%85|title=安平劍獅之旅－遍尋不著的劍獅 @ 葛瑞莉莊園 :: 痞客邦 PIXNET ::|last=(roryjen)|first=樂魚麻|newspaper=葛瑞莉莊園|accessdate=2017-01-13|language=zh-TW|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216140211/http://roryjen.pixnet.net/blog/post/27874442-%e5%ae%89%e5%b9%b3%e5%8a%8d%e7%8d%85%e4%b9%8b%e6%97%85%ef%bc%8d%e9%81%8d%e5%b0%8b%e4%b8%8d%e8%91%97%e7%9a%84%e5%8a%8d%e7%8d%85|archivedate=2017-02-16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://papilio0204.pixnet.net/blog/post/1465564-%E5%AE%89%E5%B9%B3%E5%B0%8B%E7%8D%85%E8%A8%98%EF%BC%8D%E4%BE%86%E5%88%B0%E5%AE%89%E5%B9%B3%E6%89%BE%E5%8A%8D%E7%8D%85|title=安平尋獅記－來到安平找劍獅 @ 北雁南飛－金門 :: 痞客邦 PIXNET ::|last=(papilio0204)|first=北雁南飛|newspaper=北雁南飛－金門|accessdate=2017-01-13|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2017-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113174023/http://papilio0204.pixnet.net/blog/post/1465564-%E5%AE%89%E5%B9%B3%E5%B0%8B%E7%8D%85%E8%A8%98%EF%BC%8D%E4%BE%86%E5%88%B0%E5%AE%89%E5%B9%B3%E6%89%BE%E5%8A%8D%E7%8D%85|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==由來==
獅子傳統為避邪之物，為漢人移民攜入臺灣之信仰；亦有說起自[[明朝|明]][[清朝|清]]時期水軍操練，軍人返家將刀、盾合放在家中，能令宵小卻步，而成為風尚；亦有說是居民為了紀念[[鄭成功|鄭成功]]及其軍隊<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dsps.chc.edu.tw/tuling/anc2/0qrg1.htm |title=安平劍獅 |accessdate=2017-01-13 |archive-date=2016-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224162108/http://www.dsps.chc.edu.tw/tuling/anc2/0qrg1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

